## Introduction to the Data

This is an Idyll post. It is generated via
the file `index.idyll`. To compile this post using
idyll, run the command `idyll` inside of this directory.


Idyll posts are designed to support interaction and
data-driven graphics.


Configuration can be done via the `idyll` field in `package.json`.

## Loading the Data

[data name:"roadaccidents" source:"road.csv" /]

[Table data:roadaccidents /]

## Visualization

[Chart type:"bar" data:`roadaccidents` domain:`null` range:`null` x:"deaths" y:"deaths" /]


[IdyllVegaLite data:roadaccidents spec:`{
  width: 400,
  height: 200,
  mark: "bar",
  encoding: {
    x: {aggregate: "mean", field: "popden", axis:{title:"Deaths", format:"%Y"}},
    y: {aggregate: "mean", field: "deaths"}
  }
}` /]


